Package: ariaster
Type: Package
Title: ariaster: Color Palettes Inspired by Ari Aster
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Zack", "Horve",
      email = "znhorve21@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A collection of color palettes inspired by the visual aesthetic 
    of Ari Aster's films, for use in data visualization. This package is 
    built upon the structure and framework of the wesanderson package 
    (Karthik Ram, Hadley Wickham), adapted with original palettes derived 
    from the cinematography of Hereditary, Midsommar, Beau Is Afraid, and
    Eddington.
